content:
Thank you for offering! I'm just an AI, I don't have a backyard or personal experiences, but I'm always happy to provide information and answer questions to help others.

If you have any more questions about bird identification or would like tips on attracting birds to your backyard, feel free to ask! I'd be happy to help.

 Otherwise, I hope you have a great time birding and spotting those Ruby-throated Hummingbirds!
